CircularBuffer

This is a very simple implementation of a circular buffer, the replication of
some code I probably wrote about 30+ years ago in 6809 assembler.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc CircularBuffer

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=CircularBuffer

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/CircularBuffer

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/CircularBuffer

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/CircularBuffer/


